                <h2>Product/process simulation/validation</h2>
                <p>The only alternative to the costly “over-design” and time- consuming “trial-and-error” is simulation of part
                    performance (e.g., the longevity of a welded structure) and processing (e.g., heaters/cooling lines and
                    amounts/locations of gates for the lowest cycle time of a BOP (blow-out preventer) for the Oilfield).
                    WIDL can cost-effectively build simulation knowledge for manufacturers, combining novelties in materials,
                    designs, and processes. Consequently, any know-how gained via R&D remains the property of the contractor,
                    with easy data access at any time via WIDL.</p>
            </div>
            <div id="tada1" class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
